	column 'Number of Similar Rows' = ```
			
			CALCULATE(
			    COUNTROWS(espInvoiceLine),
			    FILTER(
			        espInvoiceLine,
			        espInvoiceLine[Month Year] = EARLIER(espInvoiceLine[Month Year])
			    )
			)
			
			```
		formatString: 0
		lineageTag: dab0f96e-bc65-4558-a918-9aa524122623
		summarizeBy: sum

		annotation SummarizationSetBy = Automatic

	column 'Calculated quantity' = RELATED(cstCostEstimate[calculationquantity])/espInvoiceLine[Number of Similar Rows]
		lineageTag: 333cd189-90fd-40e1-8a52-396a5c8c810a
		summarizeBy: sum

		annotation SummarizationSetBy = Automatic

